{"id": 2289, "date": "1988-06-17T11:00:48", "date_gmt": "1988-06-17T18:00:48", "guid": {"rendered": "http://estreetshuffle.com/?p=2289"}, "modified": "2026-02-22T14:44:37", "modified_gmt": "2026-02-22T22:44:37", "slug": "meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-patti-scialfa-big-black-heaven", "status": "publish", "type": "post", "link": "https://estreetshuffle.com/index.php/1988/06/17/meeting-across-the-river-bruce-springsteen-and-patti-scialfa-big-black-heaven/", "title": {"rendered": "Big Black Heaven"}, "content": {"rendered": "<p>Patti gets the spotlight today From her 1993 debut album <em>Rumble Doll</em>, here&#8217;s &#8220;Big Black Heaven,&#8221; accompanied by Bruce on guitar and keyboards.</p>\n<div class=\"jetpack-video-wrapper\"><span class=\"embed-youtube\" style=\"text-align:center; display: block;\"><iframe loading=\"lazy\" class=\"youtube-player\" width=\"758\" height=\"427\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Um1jjOREkkg?version=3&#038;rel=1&#038;showsearch=0&#038;showinfo=1&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;fs=1&#038;hl=en-US&#038;autohide=2&#038;wmode=transparent\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" style=\"border:0;\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts allow-same-origin allow-popups allow-presentation allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox\"></iframe></span></div>\n<p>Like much of the album it comes from, &#8220;Big Black Heaven&#8221; draws heavily from Bruce&#8217;s and Patti&#8217;s relationship, mirroring the vulnerability and emotional bravery laced through Bruce&#8217;s own writing from this period.</p>\n<p><strong>Big Black Heaven</strong><br />\n<strong>Recorded:</strong> March 1993<br />\n<strong>Released:</strong>\u00a0<em>Rumble Doll\u00a0</em>(1993)<br />\n<strong>Never performed</strong></p>\n<p>\u00a9 May 26, 2018</p>\n", "protected": false}, "excerpt": {"rendered": "<p>Spotlight on Patti Scialfa today: her 1993 song &#8220;Big Black Heaven,&#8221; with Bruce on keyboards and guitar.</p>\n", "protected": false}, "author": 1, "featured_media": 2360, "comment_s